{
  "title": "About Date Plugin",
  "story": [
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "b9f4039e5a75c5b3",
      "text": "The Date Plugin marks a wiki page as a time-located event. It renders the date as a typographic display and exposes a `calendar-source` data interface consumed by the [[About Timeline Plugin]]."
    },
    {
      "type": "date",
      "id": "dad3a887165d2615",
      "text": "2026-02-01..2026-05-30 Wiki Wild Compo #Demoscene"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "055e5f5a1d86c4a9",
      "text": "## DSL"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "401ef81204f5fe9c",
      "text": "One line per event. The first matching syntax wins:\n\n| Syntax | Example |\n|---|---|\n| ISO point | `2026-01-15` |\n| ISO range | `2026-02-01..2026-05-30` |\n| Group tag | `#GroupName` |\n| Label override | `2026-02-01 My Event` |\n| Natural language | `1967 Summer of Love` |\n\nWithout a label the page title is used. The label must match a wiki page title for click-to-navigate in the Timeline Plugin."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "gj1pl92c",
      "text": "## Styles"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "8hjkevh5",
      "text": "Add `STYLE <name>` on any line to change how dates are rendered. The STYLE line is stripped before event parsing — it can appear anywhere in the item text."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "rrjw6mut",
      "text": "**STYLE TYPOGRAPHIC** (default) — large stacked day / month / year"
    },
    {
      "type": "date",
      "id": "xsnhmf9b",
      "text": "STYLE TYPOGRAPHIC\n2026-01-15 Wiki Wild Compo\n2026-02-01..2026-05-30 Demoscene Exhibition #Projects"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "vq2vdk3f",
      "text": "**STYLE PLAIN** — minimal text list, one line per event"
    },
    {
      "type": "date",
      "id": "g0lgwhk1",
      "text": "STYLE PLAIN\n2026-01-15 Wiki Wild Compo\n2026-02-01..2026-05-30 Demoscene Exhibition #Projects"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "vb97einc",
      "text": "**STYLE COMPACT** — inline pill badges"
    },
    {
      "type": "date",
      "id": "jul55qnb",
      "text": "STYLE COMPACT\n2026-01-15 Wiki Wild Compo\n2026-02-01..2026-05-30 Demoscene Exhibition #Projects"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "mhdduai7",
      "text": "**STYLE TABLE** — three-column table: date / event / group"
    },
    {
      "type": "date",
      "id": "hrdf2o11",
      "text": "STYLE TABLE\n2026-01-15 Wiki Wild Compo\n2026-02-01..2026-05-30 Demoscene Exhibition #Projects"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "d6fce2f8fd4b7000",
      "text": "## Data Interface"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "efae8b278198c00a",
      "text": "The plugin registers a `calendar-source` class and `calendarData()` method in `bind`:"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "id": "cf1cbd76a116ef58",
      "text": "$item.addClass('calendar-source')\n$item.get(0).calendarData = () => [{\n  label, start, end, span, group, page, site\n}]",
      "language": "javascript"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "eb54563c01715e64",
      "text": "Also exposes `radar-source` / `radarData()` for backwards compatibility with the Radar Plugin.\n\n## Repositories\n\n* [GitHub — wiki-plugin-date](https://github.com/Hitchhikers-Guide-to-the-Galaxy/wiki-plugin-date)\n* [npm — wiki-plugin-date](https://www.npmjs.com/package/wiki-plugin-date)"
    }
  ],
